              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 3.8 x 3.8 cm NaI(Tl) crystals for detection",
                "gamma-rays from 56Mn."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MANGB",
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The Mn-56 gamma activity was measured and",
                "the NaI detector efficiency determined at six different",
                "values for the chemical concentration of the aqueous",
                "manganese sulfate solution. The detector efficiency",
                "was determined from the absolute desintegration rate",
                "of the Mn-56 solution, which was measured with the",
                "4-Pi beta-gamma coincidence counting method."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The neutron source strength and the neutron",
                "absorption cross section ratio hydrogen/manganese were",
                "determined from the hydrogen and manganese concentra-",
                "tion ratios, the corresponding efficiencies and Mn-56",
                "activities with the straight-line fit method."
              ]
            }
          ],
